cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: Network Experiment Results for QUIC Server-Client Interactions
abstract: This dataset contains results from experiments measuring energy consumption
  during client-server interactions configured with specific network topologies (dual-path
  routing). The methodology involved setting up nodes using defined profiles, including
  different scheduling parameters. Evaluation processed these results into visualizations
  to analyze performance under various conditions.
